<p class="ql-align-justify">· CHARLIE'S TEA ·</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">「茶理宜世」</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">揭开风靡众人的“忌廉奶茶”秘技</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以“梁祝”为主题的中式古风拍照圣地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/a16e9d52069a45498590681cc2fd5de9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/dd7855be816a4f3fbdb21d8b412d8589.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">/在法律范围内，活动解释权归商家所有/</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#01</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7774e68fb3444eeba10d44a7d70179be.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/434a786ee63348499f27b0bfa9f843b3.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/3cd45992ef244ce7ae8c37943803f2c2.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/8c46f834cf21405bbc9b8f2c2dbf3a3b.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/c34cb0a6d65b484fafb8194d3eed4a47.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/690c84b0cbb3425b863ad9d0480449d4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>永庆坊门店以“梁祝”为主题，古典优雅的风格令人心情愉悦。</strong>「茶理宜世」专注于将中国传统元素与新式茶饮结合，在如今快节奏的都市生活中，<strong>重归旧时江南的惬意柔情！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/1903ffaaf97d45628b603bae31d587f3.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>永庆坊店还有一款特制的梁祝周边杯子，令人爱不释手。</strong>杯子透明中透有一丝丝粉色，还带有蝴蝶形状的装饰闪片，刹那间闪闪发亮，仿佛寓意着梁祝的爱情~</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#02</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7774e68fb3444eeba10d44a7d70179be.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>经典必喝“忌廉奶茶”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>郁郁幽兰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/d6a631bc294d4a6da5f79a6703ea2f40.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/585960c062eb4a1785dadbf1036b320d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>必点的招牌饮品！</strong>口感丰富，奶香浓郁，口感丝滑。喜欢坚果和忌廉的小伙伴一定不能错过！<strong>喝上一口，满口香浓绵密，唇齿留香。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>精选优质材料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/a7d7d1863fe343bf975554af27021853.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/44e1c82c76ce4f7794e33272044c2889.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200827/9394001553904163a938a774a506131e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>精选被誉为“斯里兰卡献给世界的礼物”美称的斯里兰卡红茶，口感细腻，回味甘甜，茶香味浓郁。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200827/3f0905affe5d472d8e1d5dba1552ec96.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">CHARLIE'S TEA</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200827/1bbc9718be2e412ab345c7b7f0bdd16d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/18a9afb6bf674990aded042bf0ce347a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>搭配维记鲜奶，味道香浓，口感丝滑，还伴有淡淡奶香味~</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/f74bb6b41f3f4f548c4dd1f6aac4912c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/d3a918da30234f83aa99fd461b74a3d9.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">\\\\\\\</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/68472bac4d9048fcb527474ac10f25fc.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>精选新西兰进口淡奶油制成的忌廉，</strong>一圈一圈地挤成小山，<strong>还有特制碧根果点缀，</strong>香脆可口，简直就是让人无法拒绝的诱惑。</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>奶香浓郁，口感丰富</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/77e6653cdcf6407ba8919af7f6ce10cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/ef29d81a407348699981658f401a5855.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200827/86a871ebd4384b1e9ba7bd866002d548.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">先吃上厚厚的忌廉，再喝上细腻醇厚的鲜奶茶，茶底与上层奶油搭配得刚刚好，口感清新的茶底中和了忌廉的甜腻，第一口就让人很惊艳！<strong>口感顺滑，不会觉得腻，让人欲罢不能！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>还可以加这些配料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/56e6c98aebe34fbfb3f09545390c24c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/60ef4a14ed934caeb6169a894f4d4ed2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/2e3b8a3fd07f4d7fa5a7d3dae9e7f451.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">还有各种配料可添加，芋圆、白玉珠珠、金珠珠、晶冻等，喜欢嚼劲的小伙伴一定不能错过！</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>梧桐</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/1d2c0de4838b48f983354d2b031b5f4d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/5ae7937dd8304d8dbf388c71bad0427e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">梧桐看似与郁郁幽兰相似，其实却大有不同，<strong>梧桐采用的是高级凤凰单枞茶底，带有独特的天然花香。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/44a4bad2fb0e4f39ade1661ccb50c598.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/f60d20fb0a864bf5ac223cc383a15513.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/cbcf9b2df731494ca35a4397393fb826.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>上层加入安佳淡奶油制作的醇厚忌廉，铺上香脆腰果果仁碎，香脆可口。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/f2b59864a99341508c8c5bab44b8a248.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/47aae44167914376903ed6518dd53510.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/1234a891a7574720a2b73a8dadadf7bc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/489979fa5f1e4fe297e456efc1033722.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">颜值也是杠杠的！拿来拍照打卡超好看！喝的时候也可以把忌廉与奶茶搅混，<strong>单枞茶香十足，略带一点点茶感，适合喜欢喝乌龙的小伙伴。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#03</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7774e68fb3444eeba10d44a7d70179be.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>还有这些也不要错过</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>烟雨乌龙</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/6f71479a078a47f0b09c5a51d9b4413a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>精选高等级白桃乌龙茶，搭配维记鲜牛奶制成，清香四溢，茶香回甘。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/8b0103e2388e44c59dbe3a800f9480d0.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200827/492bb3fc0e154a7aab5aebafc3da092a.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">\\\\\\\</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">///</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/ba737b4f3d4549a1a8767a7c08333d32.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">现打的奶泡口感细腻顺滑，喝起来一点都不腻，再撒上小麦粉点缀，透着一股香浓的茶味~</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/21df3e86074e4314bd455522068afe51.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/90fd1a50594248d28026c9409c38bf93.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>入口先是鲜奶的香醇，接着就是浓郁的乌龙香慢慢回甘，每喝一口都犹如吸了一口江南烟雨的气息...</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>卿卿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/c36513f8fc184c6aa96bd3fa36275dd5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>甄选高等级的四季青茗茶搭配维记鲜牛奶，茶香悠长，绵绵细腻。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200827/0c52e2a64ad946d9aaee7b89205d3540.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/905297000c284ec69a87917ca8c0804b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>孔雀-茉莉毛尖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200827/480135f03ef444688391381923709e12.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">由巨峰葡萄和茉莉绿茶制作的冰沙果茶，搭配新鲜葡萄果肉、芋圆和晶冻，<strong>肉嫩多汁，层次丰富。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200827/e11a052829d54c01a451ec992579a2da.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/0d9b8eb675474e2caa5fc352e4deb455.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">冰沙<strong>口感细腻清凉，绵绵潺潺</strong>，还能吸到饱满的葡萄肉，每一颗葡萄都是手工去皮去核的，<strong>啖啖丰硕多汁、沁心清甜。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>孔雀-养乐多</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/d7956cb9cc3b48a19cbb6d729fc4e3c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">精选巨峰葡萄和养乐多制作的冰沙果茶，冰沙酸甜宜人，搭配新鲜葡萄果肉、芋圆和晶冻，<strong>肉嫩多汁，层次丰富。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/130b89874b13473287a653e82f7b5969.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">\\\</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200827/3aeb0da5c4ee4352977a9ae784b52dce.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>晶莹剔透的净透仿佛把饮品悬在在空中，颜值很高！</strong>酸酸甜甜的口感融入细腻的冰沙中，沁人心肺，<strong>一口孔雀，一口夏天。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>#04</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7774e68fb3444eeba10d44a7d70179be.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>中式古风拍照圣地</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>以“梁祝”为主题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/96ad23c7495847039ba7115f57675c17.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/0fe72d038aa24323a12e50d0db725d09.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/e5ccbc16099d48129b333cfb70f92716.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">CHARLIE'S TEA</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200827/186c4fd391dc447b9cc076d5e853aae4.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">位于永庆坊的新店，是一个传统文化与光影空间的相遇，<strong>独栋的古风风格与恩宁路的西关风情相互融合。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/222cbe70b5ea4b1cb1ffcdd21b7b69cf.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/ef91868253a3421297fce37b0461b919.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/6a2f52d38a2a4e818d2b9ed25399ed3a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">以中国古代民间爱情故事《梁山伯与祝英台》为门店主题风格，店内随处可见的故事元素，<strong>很有中国古风的韵味，在这里拍照打卡别有一番风味。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/fa77c350f25142498a58487243b233c1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200827/36ccaa5cf90d4dfeaea76d15417e0578.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/75e66c9cb58543a782fd3daf811f06fd.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7986e1cd48144c0ea5635b721948a7b7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">别致的木花窗，斑驳的泥石墙，原木风的木制桌椅，尽显中式传统之美，<strong>各处绿植点缀这江南风情般的景致。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/7ded7678fca5426a84c22df1f8d472e0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/5c51eada544647c994cb8886e3343c04.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>坐在这里，品一口温柔绵密的江南茶，仿佛重归旧时江南的惬意柔情！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200827/a81c13fc9683439b84740e2d49731e14.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200827/466b40aa7c5d445e8653d1cee41eb76f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200827/4e8f508a319048209328985f93ad9898.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200827/a16e9d52069a45498590681cc2fd5de9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200827/dd7855be816a4f3fbdb21d8b412d8589.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
